EXPLANATION
BY THE LEGISLATIVE COUNCIL
OF
A N A C T
RELATING TO TAXATION -- THE PARKING SERVICES TAXATION ACT
***
1 This act would grant municipalities the authority to impose a parking services sales tax on
2 parking lots and parking structures that charge for parking services through an ordinance. The taxes
3 would be collected by the state and redistributed to the municipalities. Furthermore, this act would
4 make such revenues exempt from the total tax levy limit imposed by ยง 44-5-2.
5 This act would take effect on January 1, 2026.
